{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id79e4b7e4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s3922"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3922"},"text":"§ 3922.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Federal acquisition","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary is authorized to purchase wetlands or interests in wetlands, which are not acquired under the authority of the Migratory Bird Conservation Act of 1929 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s715–715s"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 715–715s","children":[],"tail":"), consistent with the wetlands priority conservation plan established under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s3921"},"text":"section 3921 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id79e4b7e5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/645/tIII/s304"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–645, title III, § 304","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/3588"},"text":"100 Stat. 3588","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id79e4b7e6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id79e4b7e7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id79e4b7e8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Migratory Bird Conservation Act of 1929, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1929-02-18/ch257"},"text":"act Feb. 18, 1929, ch. 257","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/45/1222"},"text":"45 Stat. 1222","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter III (§ 715 et seq.) of chapter 7 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s715"},"text":"section 715 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
